window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Ellea, a seer and trickster witch, is haunted by her past.</b></p> <p>Shunned within her community of supernaturals, she values her family and control over her destructive powers. When her visions of a terrifying future are realized and the people she loves most are threatened by her magic, Ellea flees with her familiar to Glenover, an isolated town willing to overlook her flaws. Or so she thought.</p> <p>Rosier has lived in Glenover for over five hundred years. When a curvy witch drops into his solitary life, he finds himself in an internal battle between purging the world of her dangerous magic and keeping her for himself.</p> <p>Will Ellea and Rosier destroy each other or give in to a burning attraction that has them questioning everything they know about love?</p> <p>This new dark fantasy romance has all your favorite things: shadow play, supernaturals, loveable characters, and some tricky magic.</p>"; 
